      <title>随着低收入美国人的消费减少，主要食品公司提供优惠和新尺寸</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/major-food-companies-offering-deals-new-sizes-low-income-americans-spend-less-2024-04-08/</link>
